content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Viewing One-Time Reports Use the One-time Reports screen to view previously generated one-time reports. Procedure Go to Detections → Reports → One-time Reports. The One-time Reports screen appears. Click the View link in the View column for the generated report you want to view.
